      "description": "The Bitwise MSTR Option Income Strategy ETF (IMST) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in information technology equity. The fund seeks to provide monthly income and capped gains on the MicroStrategy Incorporated stock (MSTR) through a synthetic covered call strategy, collateralized by cash and US Treasurys. The actively managed fund uses both standardized exchange-traded and FLEX options. IMST was launched on Apr 1, 2025 and is issued by Bitwise.",
